* pre-Go 1

- weekly releases
- spec still moving
- no stability promise, packages very much still in flux
- but code usually fixed easily with gofix

* Go 1

- spec set in stone until Go 2 -> *stability* promise: [[https://golang.org/doc/go1compat]]
